<p>The <b>history of the Scots language</b> refers to how <a href="Old_English" title="Old English">Anglic</a> <a href="Variety_(linguistics)" title="Variety (linguistics)">varieties</a> spoken in parts of <a href="Scotland" title="Scotland">Scotland</a> developed into modern <a href="Scots_language" title="Scots language">Scots</a>.</p>
